channel.title: In Time - Winter J Studios (SynthWave)
channel.description:
Hello everyone!
Today I have a new special SynthWave track. Thought I might get into the genre since we got the new sounds. It’s a slow beat with a nice smoothing melody.
It’s a short song but hopefully i get awesome feedback! Tell me what you think!
Soundcloud: [In Time - Winter J. Studios](https://soundcloud.com/winter_j_studios/in-time-winter-j-studios)
